      <item>
        <title>Customizing console log output</title>
        <description>&lt;amp-img width=&quot;2170&quot; height=&quot;664&quot; sizes=&quot;100vw&quot; src=&quot;/assets/postimages/console-output.png&quot; alt=&quot;console.log text customization&quot;&gt;&lt;/amp-img&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Open console and copy and paste the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;
  &lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot; data-lang=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;%c ♥ %cweb %cdev%celop%cment %c:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: red; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: #f36f21; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: #000; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: #f36f21; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: #000; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;background: #ddd; color: red; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;'&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or make rainbow text with the &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7505623/colors-in-javascript-console/21457293#21457293&quot;&gt;example from StackOverflow&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
